<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Customers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .customer-group {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .customer-group h2 {
            color: #555;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Customers</h1>
        
        <div class="customer-group">
            <h2>Elderly Residents</h2>
            <p>We provide compassionate care for the elderly, ensuring they receive the support they need to maintain dignity and independence in their daily lives.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-group">
            <h2>Individuals with Disabilities</h2>
            <p>We support individuals with physical and learning disabilities, helping them navigate daily activities and achieve a fulfilling quality of life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-group">
            <h2>Residents with Dementia</h2>
            <p>Our tailored approach ensures residents with dementia receive personalized care, promoting comfort, familiarity, and engagement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-group">
            <h2>Young Mothers in Need</h2>
            <p>Through our volunteer work, we provide guidance and support to young mothers, particularly those caring for children with special needs.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
